Yakult Probiotic Drink 80ml is a sweetened probiotic milk beverage fermented with the bacteria strain Lacticaseibacillus paracasei strain Shirota (LcS). Each 80ml bottle contains over 8 billion live LcS bacteria, which are known to support digestive health by improving the balance of intestinal flora.
Type of Milk: Cultured Probiotic Milk Drink
Ideal For: Individuals seeking to support digestive health and maintain a balanced gut flora
Ingredients: Water Sugar Skim milk powder Glucose Flavors Lacticaseibacillus paracasei strain Shirota (LcS)
Storage: Keep refrigerated
Where to buy: SM Supermarket Makati, Robinsons Supermarket Manila
______________________________________________________________________________

Protein: 1g
Carbohydrates: 14g
Fat: 0g
Calcium: 40mg
Potassium: 50mg
